miscellaneous tools for molecular biology.

** Commands

seqview: render overview image of sequence, primers, bisulfite sequence results.
bisearch: design primer based on primer3 algorithm.
primers: calculate primer properties
virtualpcr: PCR primer alignment tool using bowtie

** Install
python setup.py install

** develop
/opt/local/bin/virtualenv-2.7 environ
source environ/bin/activate
pip install numpy
python setup.py develop

** Mac OS X, homebrew and python Environment

*** Installing Brew's python
http://penandpants.com/2012/02/24/install-python/
https://github.com/mxcl/homebrew/wiki/Homebrew-and-Python

% which python
/usr/bin/python
% python --version
Python 2.7.1
% brew install python
% which python
/usr/local/bin/python
% sudo easy_install virtualenv
% virtualenv --version
1.8.2
% which virtualenv
/usr/local/share/python/virtualenv
% pip install numpy

% brew install gfortran
% pip install scipy
  --> failed. ;-P

*** virtualenv setup

% virtualenv env
New python executable in env/bin/python
Installing setuptools............done.
Installing pip...............done.
% source env/bin/activate   
(env)% python setup.py develop 
  --> numpy compile failed ;-PPP
(env)% pip install numpy
  --> success
(env)% python setup.py develop 
...
Using /Users/mizuy/projects/seqtool/env/lib/python2.7/site-packages
Finished processing dependencies for seqtool==0.1.1


